      "text": "Tee irr nepeetizzigi prett to\nKUNGU turrejschees/ jo tee irr\nfweſchns Behrnus dsemdinaj-\nschi/ nu norths tohs tas jauns\nMehnes ar winnu Dattahm.\n"
